ns the further result that the level N\ngenus is invariant under the blow up along a submanifold Y of a complex\nmanifold X if the codimension of Y in X is congruent 1 modulo N.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2004 22:15:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
